You have to make your container as relative :

    .container {
        position: relative;
    }

And make the inputs to the position as absolutes:


      .top-left {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: -20px;
      }
      
      .top-right {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        right: -20px;
      }
      
      .bottom-right {
       position: absolute;
       bottom: 0;
       right: -20px;
      }
      
      .bottom-left {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: -20px;
      }

