Absolute positioned checkboxes will help you solve your problem.

      .top-left,
      .top-right,
      .bottom-left,
      .bottom-right {
        position: absolute;
        margin: 0;
      }
      
      .top-left {
        top: 0;
        left: -1em;
      }

Don&#39;t forget to position your wrapping container relatively. Otherwise absolute positioning won&#39;t work properly since absolute positions are always absolute to their next relative parent.

